About this game

The aim of the game is to keep the ball on the board. Click to place cubes, control the ball and prevent it from escaping.
Small balls are bonuses, get them to get boosters.

There's 7 types of boosters:
Blue: Unlimited blocks
Yellow: Walls
Pink: Blocks along the sides
Green: Block rain
Orange: Bigger ball
Gray: Unbreakable blocks
Black: Triple ball

Relax and enjoy the music as the ball bounces!
How long can you resist?

Luuk Domhof

July 10, 2020
Great idea with great mechanics, but could use some work in the art and polish departments. Perhaps it'd cool to earn money/credits for the time you survive which would allow you to buy upgrades? Better walls, faster building, 2 walls at once etc. Also, there's no support for multi finger input. Using 2 fingers at once causes you to place a block in the middle of your two fingers. This could be improved by only using the first finger that hit for example. Other than that highly enjoyable!
